{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">通过实验认识浮力，探究浮力的大小跟哪些因素有关</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">浮力</span>=<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">重力</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">-</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">拉力</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">弹簧测力计、钩码</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个、盛水烧杯、盛盐水烧杯</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.探究浮力的大小是否跟物体浸没的深度有关。</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 把弹簧测力计下悬挂的物体浸没在一种液体中，并分别停在液体内不同的深度，观察弹簧测力计的示数是否不同，由此确定浮力的大小是否跟浸没的深度有关。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">探究浮力的大小是否跟物体浸在液体中的体积有关？</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 把物体悬挂在弹簧测力计下，当物体浸在液体中的体积逐渐增大时，弹簧测力计的示数是否变化？若有变化，它是增大的还是减小的？这说明什么问题？</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">浮力的大小是否跟液体的密度有关？</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 把悬挂在测力计下的同一物体先后浸没在两种液体中，看看浮力的大小是否跟液体的密度有关。若有关，有怎样的定性关系？</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">物体在液体中所受浮力的大小，跟它浸在液体中的体积有关、跟液体的密度有关。物体浸在液体中的体积越大、液体的密度越大，浮力就越大</span></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">物体受到的浮力与物体在水中的深度无关，跟物体的形状无关。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}